    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith's request to the partners",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of Opposition and United People's Power Sajith Premadasa met the leaders of nine partner parties this afternoon.",
        "On behalf of the United People's Shakti, the party's general secretary Ranjith Mathumabandara and many members of parliament including Puthika Pathirana have participated.",
        "Vimal Weerawansa, Udaya Kammanpila, Vasudeva Nanayakkara, Kalanithi G Weerasinghe, Premanath Tolawatta, Weerasumana Weerasinghe, Kevindu Kumarathunga, Asanga Navaratna also participated in the meeting on behalf of the partner parties.",
        "Sajith Premadasa has requested the party leaders to support him as he will participate in the presidential poll."
      ],
